{"word":"G1640 - ἐλάσσων - elássōn - el-as'-sone - Less","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐλάσσων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">elássōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">el-as'-sone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Less</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"இளைய, சிறிய, குறைந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"less"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Compound of the same as <a href=\"#/G1646 - ἐλάχιστος - eláchistos - el-akh'-is-tos/1646\">G1646</a>; <i>smaller</i> (in size, quantity, age or quality): - less, under, worse, younger.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}